{"word":"σφετερίζω","slug":"σφετερίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σφετερίζω</b></el> <el>(σφετερίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σφέτερος'><el>σφέτερος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to make one's own, appropriate, usurp</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—so, as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>σφετερίζομαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}